        # easy-getch
        Easily get a single character.
        
        Inspired by [this article](https://code.activestate.com/recipes/134892).
        
        ## Installation
        ```bash
        pip install easy_getch
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```Python
        from easy_getch import getch
        
        ch = getch()
        print(ch)
        ```
